metadata.description: FROM THE SHADOWZ - GOLD MIXTAPE | SIDE A: https://shadowzverse.io/nfts/fromtheshadowz/goldmixtape/GOLD_MIXTAPE_SIDE_A.mp3 / SIDE B: https://shadowzverse.io/nfts/fromtheshadowz/goldmixtape/GOLD_MIXTAPE_SIDE_B.mp3 | Live from the SHADOWZVERSE comes an eclectic mixtape from some of the most talented musicians in WEB3. In collaboration with the SOUTHERN EMPIRE, From The Shadowz Vol.1 is an experimental NFT hybrid blending music and art across 9 unique tracks that all inhabit a single collection.
